name: Interdimensional Landscape #3
description:
How do we se the unseeable?

I often wonder how other dimensions might look like if we were there to see them. This images are the result of a generative art experiment using live feed and real-time particle reaction in order to create a "photographical" omage of an alternative reality that might or might not be there. 

Diego Escobar is a colombian multidisciplinar artist graduated from Universidad de los Andes. Photography, Drawing and New Media Art, are his primary creation fields
